{"schema_version":"1.7.3","id":"OESA-2024-2237","published":"2024-10-12T11:09:20Z","modified":"2025-09-03T06:18:35.540713Z","upstream":["CVE-2022-45063"],"summary":"xterm security update","details":"The xterm program is a terminal emulator for the X Window System. It provides DEC VT102 and Tektronix 4014 compatible terminals.\r\n\r\nSecurity Fix(es):\r\n\r\nxterm before 375 allows code execution via font ops, e.g., because an OSC 50 response may have Ctrl-g and therefore lead to command execution within the vi line-editing mode of Zsh. NOTE: font ops are not allowed in the xterm default configurations of some Linux distributions.(CVE-2022-45063)","affected":[{"package":{"name":"xterm","ecosystem":"openEuler:22.03-LTS-SP1","purl":"pkg:rpm/openEuler/xterm&distro=openEuler-22.03-LTS-SP1"},"ranges":[{"type":"ECOSYSTEM","events":[{"introduced":"0"},{"fixed":"363-6.oe2203sp1"}]}],"ecosystem_specific":{"aarch64":["xterm-363-6.oe2203sp1.aarch64.rpm","xterm-debuginfo-363-6.oe2203sp1.aarch64.rpm","xterm-debugsource-363-6.oe2203sp1.aarch64.rpm","xterm-help-363-6.oe2203sp1.aarch64.rpm"],"src":["xterm-363-6.oe2203sp1.src.rpm"],"x86_64":["xterm-363-6.oe2203sp1.x86_64.rpm","xterm-debuginfo-363-6.oe2203sp1.x86_64.rpm","xterm-debugsource-363-6.oe2203sp1.x86_64.rpm","xterm-help-363-6.oe2203sp1.x86_64.rpm"]},"database_specific":{"source":"https://repo.openeuler.org/security/data/osv/OESA-2024-2237.json"}}],"references":[{"type":"ADVISORY","url":"https://www.openeuler.org/zh/security/security-bulletins/detail/?id=openEuler-SA-2024-2237"},{"type":"ADVISORY","url":"https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-2022-45063"}],"database_specific":{"severity":"Critical"}}